  "keyFeatures": [
    "Three elemental magic schools: Water, Earth, and Air",
    "18 unique elemental spells with custom effects and animations",
    "Tiered armor sets with elemental-specific bonuses",
    "Elemental staffs and wands with spell power attributes",
    "Custom status effects like Stone Flesh, Tornado, and Bubble Foam",
    "Multi-loader support for Fabric and NeoForge",
    "Integration with Spell Engine and RPG Series mods",
    "Configurable equipment stats and effect parameters"
